{"tid":167849,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[圖文漫畫］我現的工作是幫某公司的吉祥物畫網絡漫畫","createTime":"2017-03-23T06:26:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T08:12:41.000Z","uid":32526,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"251e5812a3c951e1115b6429c8b32203cff3c970","tid":167849,"uid":32526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T06:26:36.000Z","msg":"我現的工作是幫某公司的吉祥物畫網頁圖文漫畫<br />\n(除此之外，工作也包括了吉祥物的各種設計和插畫）<br />\n有些漫畫是幫公司宣傳的，但大部份都是畫自己的想畫的東西<br />\n<br />\n這份工作的內容是幫公司一天想兩篇漫畫<br />\n老實說，每篇漫畫都絞盡了我腦汁<br />\n朋友總是跟我說不要老是把自己費盡心機想到的點子這麼簡單就奉獻給公司<br />\n就算隻公仔出了名，功勞也不會記在你的份上<br />\n我卻覺得....有人打本給你畫自己想畫的東西也不壞<br />\n<br />\n真的很想很想讓外界看到我的圖文故事<br />\n縱使不留意我、不留下一個like也好，也想把故事分享給大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MOKb945.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMOKb945.jpg&h=5a5f2ede&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMYYBD0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMYYBD0.jpg&h=617eba28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0KSV897.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0KSV897.jpg&h=097cafde&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/23/141516_2055dd71952014053c27f416cab139a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F23%2F141516_2055dd71952014053c27f416cab139a1.jpg&h=47bef11f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/23/141518_1d7f32288e9e6e620b5888d3eb51aa87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F23%2F141518_1d7f32288e9e6e620b5888d3eb51aa87.jpg&h=6125f6b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果有興趣可以上去facebook page看看其他漫畫<br />\n當畫功成熟後，希望能用自己的名義去創作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.c